of misrepresentation deukmejian said 
the other initiatives however have lacked star appeal the 
celebrities didnt offer and the campaigns didnt call 
were just not trying to sell it that way said bob schmidt 
with the gas tax initiative proposition 111 and a companion 
measure proposition 108 frankly in any of the strategy 
conferences weve never even discussed getting any celebrity 
types 
