<TEXT>
frightened residents of this jungle town 
spent their second night in the streets after earthquakeprone 
perus deadliest temblor in two decades killed at least 115 people 
and injured hundreds more 
hundreds of people crowded into riojas central plaza afraid to 
enter their damaged homes many lay inside tents or beneath 
umbrellas while others crowded around smoky cooking fires in the 
