negotiating to sell military expertise without a license the 
actual sale of expertise and the unlawful sale of equipment such 
as weapons belts and night gunscopes 
such actions violate a 1986 law on the export of israeli goods 
and services and a 1956 law on the activities of reservists the 
charge sheet says 
