social security finance economy and transport reached agreement on 
the workers demands issued in a may 23 communique 
the demands included a 50 percent salary hike and retroactive 
payment of night shifts for the past three years 
unions at romanias largest steel plant in the port of galati 
said the length of the strike was beginning to affect the national 
economy noting their plant was running out of coal and limestone 
sailors dockers harbor workers and administrators struck in the 
danube ports of galati sulina tulcea cernavoda and braila 
