president bush and soviet president mikhail s 
gorbachev on thursday directed their top diplomatic aides to meet 
next week to seek a postsummit agreement on the military face of a 
united germany 
a meeting between secretary of state james a baker iii and 
soviet foreign minister eduard a shevardnadze was set for tuesday 
in copenhagen after bush and gorbachev reached an impasse on 
