television ad that shows a wooded scene with flowers blooming and 
birds chirping it then shifts to a bulletriddled photo of helms 
nailed to a tree and closes with a blob of mud hitting the picture 
a voice then says isnt it nice that mike easley and harvey gantt 
arent running negative campaigns 
